# {{component_name}} Troubleshooting Guide

Use this skill when diagnosing incidents or unexpected behavior.

## Step 1: Check Error Rate

```
query_metrics("rate({{prometheus_namespace}}_http_requests_total{status=~'5..'}[5m])")
```

If error rate is elevated, proceed to Step 2.

## Step 2: Search Recent Errors

```
search_logs("level:ERROR", time_range="15m")
```

Look for patterns: repeated exceptions, timeout errors, dependency failures.

